text: Fabiana Hurtado Tarrazona (born 1998) is a Bolivian beauty pageant titleholder who won Miss Bolivia 2019. as Miss Bolivia, She represented Bolivia at the Miss Universe 2019 competition. == Pageantry == === Miss Bolivia 2019 === Hurtado began her pageantry career when she represented San Ignacio de Velasco to compete for the title of Miss Santa Cruz 2019 before eventually participating at Miss Bolivia 2019. She won the crown and an award at the conclusion of the final night; Miss Sports. On June 29, 2019. She was crowned as Miss Universe Bolivia 2019 and being the eventual winner of Miss Bolivia 2019. She was crowned by the outgoing titleholder, Joyce Prado. === Miss Universe 2019 === As Miss Bolivia, Hurtado represented Bolivia at the Miss Universe 2019 competition but failed to place. == References == Category:Miss Universe 2019 contestants Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Bolivian beauty pageant winners
